Given an integer n. Write a program to print all the divisors of n in a single line.

Examples:

Input: n = 12
Output: 1 2 3 4 6 12
Explanation: 12 is divisible by 1 2 3 4 6 12.
Input: n = 10
Output: 1 2 5 10
Explanation: 10 is divisible by 1 2 5 10.
Constraints:
1 <= n <= 105

class Solution {
    void printDivisors(int n) {
        // code here
        for(int i=1; i<=n; i++){
            if(n%i==0){
                System.out.print(i+" ");
            }
        }
    }
}
